<h2 id="download" style="text-align:center;border-bottom:none;padding-bottom:0">Download Sonic Unleashed Recompiled</h2>

<p><strong>Version 1.0.3</strong> includes the installer application. You will need your own <strong>Xbox 360 game files</strong> (US or EU region only — Japanese and PS3 files are not compatible). DLC files are optional but highly recommended: they improve lighting textures across the game and unlock additional stages.</p>

